{
  "stem": "1530.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "More like upper class, or you know, we just--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of importance.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of importance.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think we lived a nice life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just loved Kisvarda.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a little girl, and I had loads of friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went to a very good, private school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, there's no place like Kisvarda--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and I never want to leave it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whereas, my older sisters, as they got older, they all wanted to go to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody in the world, but I-- just give me Kisvarda.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very well known in my little town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--could be with the surrounding community--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--not just Kisvarda.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I think that they brought them all in the Kisvarda ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I think that maybe Kisvarda and vicinity--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--had 3,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well actually--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was his main occupation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He would buy up vineyards before they even picked the grapes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- under our house we had a giant basement with giant vats of wine, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the smaller dealers would come from the country and buy wine from my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From the country?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You mean even towns that were smaller?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The towns were very much smaller.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they all had a bar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this wasn't kosher wine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this was for the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later on, my father always ex-- exported to Switzerland, I think Holland, and maybe Denmark, wine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not all the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It depends.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a big business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If the wine came in successfully--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if not, well, we had a little economic problem, like every business has its ups and downs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were a large family.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
